<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.10">
<l>vārā varuvāy varumeṉ māyā māyā mūrttiyā</l>
<l>yārā vamutā yaṭiyē ṉāvi yakamē tittippāy</l>
<l>tīrā viṉaika ṭīra veṉṉai yāṇṭāy tirukkuṭantai</l>
<l>yūrā yuṉakkāṭpaṭṭu maṭiyē ṉiṉṉa muḻalvēṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without coming you will come, my miraculous, miraculous form.</l>
<l>Never-sating ambrosia, you are sweet inside the soul of me, [your] servant.</l>
<l>You who ruled me so that [my] undending karma ended, you whose town is sacred</l> 
<l>Kuṭantai, will I, [your] servant who is servant to you, roam yet again?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
